  ('e_0778', 'p_g00', 'billing@example.com', 'September invoice — line item discrepancy', '<p>Hi team — our September invoice came in $1,840 above last month and we can''t reconcile the overage line. Can someone walk us through how the seat-add prorations were calculated? Looping in Tomas from finance.</p>', 'Hi team — our September invoice came in $1,840 above last month and we can''t reconcile the overage line. Can someone walk us through how the seat-add prorations were calculated? Looping in Tomas from finance.', '{}', '<e_0778@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1077909), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1077909), '[{"email":"tomas.reiner@acme.co","name":"Tomas Reiner"},{"email":"fiona.boyle@legal.acme.co","name":"Fiona Boyle"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"}]', 'c_23674901c1ffe4ef'),
  ('e_0779', 'p_g01', 'billing@example.com', 'Re: September invoice — line item discrepancy', '<p>Adding context from finance: we added 12 seats on Sep 9 and 6 more on Sep 22. Both moves should have prorated against the annual term, not been billed at full month.</p>', 'Adding context from finance: we added 12 seats on Sep 9 and 6 more on Sep 22. Both moves should have prorated against the annual term, not been billed at full month.', '{}', '<e_0779@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1086891), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1086891), '[{"email":"elena.varga@acme.co","name":"Elena Varga"},{"email":"fiona.boyle@legal.acme.co","name":"Fiona Boyle"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"}]', 'c_23674901c1ffe4ef'),
  ('e_0780', 'p_g00', 'billing@example.com', 'Re: September invoice — line item discrepancy', '<p>Legacy annual, signed in March. Happy to forward the contract if helpful.</p>', 'Legacy annual, signed in March. Happy to forward the contract if helpful.', '{}', '<e_0780@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1004986), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1004986), '[{"email":"tomas.reiner@acme.co","name":"Tomas Reiner"},{"email":"fiona.boyle@legal.acme.co","name":"Fiona Boyle"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"}]', 'c_23674901c1ffe4ef'),
  ('e_0781', 'p_g02', 'billing@example.com', 'Re: September invoice — line item discrepancy', '<p>Hi all — Fiona from Acme legal, just looped in. Before we close this out, can we get the credit memo in writing? Our auditors flag verbal credits.</p>', 'Hi all — Fiona from Acme legal, just looped in. Before we close this out, can we get the credit memo in writing? Our auditors flag verbal credits.', '{}', '<e_0781@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 792325), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 792325), '[{"email":"elena.varga@acme.co","name":"Elena Varga"},{"email":"tomas.reiner@acme.co","name":"Tomas Reiner"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"}]', 'c_23674901c1ffe4ef'),
