  ('e_0783', 'p_g03', 'sales@example.com', 'DPA redlines for Hooli expansion', '<p>Sending over our redlines on the DPA for the expansion order. Most of the changes are in section 4 (sub-processors) and section 9 (audit rights). Marina from outside counsel is CC''d.</p>', 'Sending over our redlines on the DPA for the expansion order. Most of the changes are in section 4 (sub-processors) and section 9 (audit rights). Marina from outside counsel is CC''d.', '{}', '<e_0783@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1276468), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1276468), '[{"email":"darius.weiss@hooli.com","name":"Darius Weiss"},{"email":"marina.flores@legal.acme.co","name":"Marina Flores"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_2e5f79460d968c6f'),
  ('e_0784', 'p_g05', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: DPA redlines for Hooli expansion', '<p>Hi — Marina here. The unannounced audit clause is non-negotiable for our regulated customers, but we can scope it to a 30-day notice for non-regulated tenants. Would that work?</p>', 'Hi — Marina here. The unannounced audit clause is non-negotiable for our regulated customers, but we can scope it to a 30-day notice for non-regulated tenants. Would that work?', '{}', '<e_0784@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1155038), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1155038), '[{"email":"harriet.cole@hooli.com","name":"Harriet Cole"},{"email":"darius.weiss@hooli.com","name":"Darius Weiss"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_2e5f79460d968c6f'),
  ('e_0785', 'p_g04', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: DPA redlines for Hooli expansion', '<p>Jumping in — Darius from procurement at Hooli. Once legal aligns, I''ll need the final DPA in our vendor portal before we can countersign the order form. Just flagging the dependency.</p>', 'Jumping in — Darius from procurement at Hooli. Once legal aligns, I''ll need the final DPA in our vendor portal before we can countersign the order form. Just flagging the dependency.', '{}', '<e_0785@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1051779), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1051779), '[{"email":"harriet.cole@hooli.com","name":"Harriet Cole"},{"email":"marina.flores@legal.acme.co","name":"Marina Flores"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_2e5f79460d968c6f'),
  ('e_0786', 'p_g05', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: DPA redlines for Hooli expansion', '<p>Reviewed. One small edit on the sub-processor list (we''re flagging Resend as a notification trigger only, not a primary processor). Otherwise good to sign.</p>', 'Reviewed. One small edit on the sub-processor list (we''re flagging Resend as a notification trigger only, not a primary processor). Otherwise good to sign.', '{}', '<e_0786@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 852105), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 852105), '[{"email":"harriet.cole@hooli.com","name":"Harriet Cole"},{"email":"darius.weiss@hooli.com","name":"Darius Weiss"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_2e5f79460d968c6f'),
  ('e_0787', 'p_g03', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: DPA redlines for Hooli expansion', '<p>Signed and uploaded. Order form follows in a separate thread.</p>', 'Signed and uploaded. Order form follows in a separate thread.', '{}', '<e_0787@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 522441), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 522441), '[{"email":"darius.weiss@hooli.com","name":"Darius Weiss"},{"email":"marina.flores@legal.acme.co","name":"Marina Flores"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_2e5f79460d968c6f'),
  ('e_0788', 'p_g06', 'sales@example.com', 'SAML SSO requirements for Q1 rollout', '<p>We''re targeting a Q1 rollout. Need to confirm SAML SSO covers SCIM provisioning, JIT user creation, and per-inbox group mapping. Sienna and Noor from our security team are CC''d.</p>', 'We''re targeting a Q1 rollout. Need to confirm SAML SSO covers SCIM provisioning, JIT user creation, and per-inbox group mapping. Sienna and Noor from our security team are CC''d.', '{}', '<e_0788@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1563545), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1563545), '[{"email":"sienna.holt@piedpiper.ai","name":"Sienna Holt"},{"email":"noor.haddad@piedpiper.ai","name":"Noor Haddad"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_2aebcd892cd20faf'),
  ('e_0789', 'p_g07', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: SAML SSO requirements for Q1 rollout', '<p>Quick clarification on JIT: when a user is deprovisioned upstream, how fast does access revoke on your side? We need < 5 minute SLA for SOC 2.</p>', 'Quick clarification on JIT: when a user is deprovisioned upstream, how fast does access revoke on your side? We need < 5 minute SLA for SOC 2.', '{}', '<e_0789@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1529082), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1529082), '[{"email":"rajiv.kapur@piedpiper.ai","name":"Rajiv Kapur"},{"email":"noor.haddad@piedpiper.ai","name":"Noor Haddad"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_2aebcd892cd20faf'),
  ('e_0790', 'p_g08', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: SAML SSO requirements for Q1 rollout', '<p>Yes please on the SOC 2 report. Also — what''s the disaster-recovery story for the SAML metadata itself? If your IdP-facing endpoint goes down, do we get cached metadata?</p>', 'Yes please on the SOC 2 report. Also — what''s the disaster-recovery story for the SAML metadata itself? If your IdP-facing endpoint goes down, do we get cached metadata?', '{}', '<e_0790@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1446150), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1446150), '[{"email":"rajiv.kapur@piedpiper.ai","name":"Rajiv Kapur"},{"email":"sienna.holt@piedpiper.ai","name":"Sienna Holt"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_2aebcd892cd20faf'),
  ('e_0791', 'p_g06', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: SAML SSO requirements for Q1 rollout', '<p>Received. Looks good on our end. One more thing — can we get a sandbox tenant to test the SCIM bridge before we cutover?</p>', 'Received. Looks good on our end. One more thing — can we get a sandbox tenant to test the SCIM bridge before we cutover?', '{}', '<e_0791@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1168892), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1168892), '[{"email":"sienna.holt@piedpiper.ai","name":"Sienna Holt"},{"email":"noor.haddad@piedpiper.ai","name":"Noor Haddad"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_2aebcd892cd20faf'),
  ('e_0792', 'p_g07', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: SAML SSO requirements for Q1 rollout', '<p>Tested SCIM — works. We''re moving forward with the Q1 plan. Will send the signed order form tomorrow.</p>', 'Tested SCIM — works. We''re moving forward with the Q1 plan. Will send the signed order form tomorrow.', '{}', '<e_0792@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 1, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 724911), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 724911), '[{"email":"rajiv.kapur@piedpiper.ai","name":"Rajiv Kapur"},{"email":"noor.haddad@piedpiper.ai","name":"Noor Haddad"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_2aebcd892cd20faf'),
  ('e_0793', 'p_g09', 'sales@example.com', 'Vendor security questionnaire', '<p>Hi — Priya from Globex procurement. Attaching our vendor security questionnaire (97 questions, sorry). Need it back by EOW to keep the renewal on track.</p>', 'Hi — Priya from Globex procurement. Attaching our vendor security questionnaire (97 questions, sorry). Need it back by EOW to keep the renewal on track.', '{}', '<e_0793@example.test>', 'pass', 'pass', 'pass', 0, (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 779971), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 779971), '[{"email":"kenji.yamada@globex.io","name":"Kenji Yamada"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"}]', 'c_f25856779ecd28f1'),
