  ('s_0053', 'p_g06', 'rajiv.kapur@piedpiper.ai', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: SAML SSO requirements for Q1 rollout', '<p>All three are supported on Enterprise. SCIM via Okta/Azure, JIT is on by default, and group mapping is per-tenant configurable. Happy to walk through the admin UI on a call.</p>', 'All three are supported on Enterprise. SCIM via Okta/Azure, JIT is on by default, and group mapping is per-tenant configurable. Happy to walk through the admin UI on a call.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1618735), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1618735), '[{"email":"sienna.holt@piedpiper.ai","name":"Sienna Holt"},{"email":"noor.haddad@piedpiper.ai","name":"Noor Haddad"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_2aebcd892cd20faf'),
