  ('s_0060', 'p_g11', 'alec.briggs@northwind.co', 'support@example.com', 'Re: Follow-up on Tuesday''s outage — RCA needed', '<p>Understood — sorry for the impact. RCA is being drafted now; expect it by Friday. Re: the lost messages: those should be in our retry queue, will confirm and replay them today.</p>', 'Understood — sorry for the impact. RCA is being drafted now; expect it by Friday. Re: the lost messages: those should be in our retry queue, will confirm and replay them today.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 505320), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 505320), '[{"email":"irina.popov@northwind.co","name":"Irina Popov"},{"email":"mateo.santos@northwind.co","name":"Mateo Santos"},{"email":"sam@example.com","name":"Sam Liu"}]', 'c_244601dab22d17a1'),
  ('s_0061', 'p_g12', 'irina.popov@northwind.co', 'support@example.com', 'Re: Follow-up on Tuesday''s outage — RCA needed', '<p>Replay completed at 14:32 UTC. 3,841 messages restored, 159 were over the 7-day retry window and we''re investigating those manually.</p>', 'Replay completed at 14:32 UTC. 3,841 messages restored, 159 were over the 7-day retry window and we''re investigating those manually.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 353853), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 353853), '[{"email":"alec.briggs@northwind.co","name":"Alec Briggs"},{"email":"mateo.santos@northwind.co","name":"Mateo Santos"},{"email":"sam@example.com","name":"Sam Liu"}]', 'c_244601dab22d17a1'),
  ('s_0062', 'p_g13', 'mateo.santos@northwind.co', 'support@example.com', 'Re: Follow-up on Tuesday''s outage — RCA needed', '<p>Sent the breakdown via secure share. Most are from two partners; one partner''s retry config was overly aggressive and exhausted before our backend recovered.</p>', 'Sent the breakdown via secure share. Most are from two partners; one partner''s retry config was overly aggressive and exhausted before our backend recovered.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 317979), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 317979), '[{"email":"alec.briggs@northwind.co","name":"Alec Briggs"},{"email":"irina.popov@northwind.co","name":"Irina Popov"},{"email":"sam@example.com","name":"Sam Liu"}]', 'c_244601dab22d17a1'),
  ('s_0063', 'p_g14', 'jana.kowalski@stark.industries', 'hello@example.com', 'Re: Stark onboarding — kickoff next steps', '<p>Welcome! Sent a calendar hold for Tuesday 10am PT. Runbook attached — it covers the three migration phases and the rollback path.</p>', 'Welcome! Sent a calendar hold for Tuesday 10am PT. Runbook attached — it covers the three migration phases and the rollback path.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1011930), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1011930), '[{"email":"ravi.menon@stark.industries","name":"Ravi Menon"},{"email":"lucia.fernandez@stark.industries","name":"Lucia Fernandez"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"}]', 'c_7b2fe860ab89bc71'),
  ('s_0064', 'p_g15', 'ravi.menon@stark.industries', 'hello@example.com', 'Re: Stark onboarding — kickoff next steps', '<p>Single-region for phase 1 (US-East), multi-region added in phase 3 once we''ve validated the inbound flow. Splitting that out keeps the rollback simple.</p>', 'Single-region for phase 1 (US-East), multi-region added in phase 3 once we''ve validated the inbound flow. Splitting that out keeps the rollback simple.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 945257), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 945257), '[{"email":"jana.kowalski@stark.industries","name":"Jana Kowalski"},{"email":"lucia.fernandez@stark.industries","name":"Lucia Fernandez"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"}]', 'c_7b2fe860ab89bc71'),
  ('s_0065', 'p_g16', 'lucia.fernandez@stark.industries', 'hello@example.com', 'Re: Stark onboarding — kickoff next steps', '<p>Either works. If you keep DNS, we''ll provide the records and timing; if you hand off, we manage it via a temporary delegation. Most enterprise customers prefer to keep it.</p>', 'Either works. If you keep DNS, we''ll provide the records and timing; if you hand off, we manage it via a temporary delegation. Most enterprise customers prefer to keep it.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 807040), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 807040), '[{"email":"jana.kowalski@stark.industries","name":"Jana Kowalski"},{"email":"ravi.menon@stark.industries","name":"Ravi Menon"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"}]', 'c_7b2fe860ab89bc71'),
  ('s_0066', 'p_g18', 'hugo.lefevre@umbrella.med', 'support@example.com', 'Re: Chat-mode UI for support inboxes — feedback', '<p>Great feedback — keyboard nav is on the roadmap for next sprint, sound toggles we can ship behind a flag this week, and roster-change UI is shipping today actually (RosterDiffNotice component, will appear inline).</p>', 'Great feedback — keyboard nav is on the roadmap for next sprint, sound toggles we can ship behind a flag this week, and roster-change UI is shipping today actually (RosterDiffNotice component, will appear inline).', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1353938), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1353938), '[{"email":"deepa.rao@umbrella.med","name":"Deepa Rao"},{"email":"anika.osei@umbrella.med","name":"Anika Osei"},{"email":"petr.zelinka@umbrella.med","name":"Petr Zelinka"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_1a81a93e429517f7'),
  ('s_0067', 'p_g19', 'anika.osei@umbrella.med', 'support@example.com', 'Re: Chat-mode UI for support inboxes — feedback', '<p>Inline pill above the message that triggered the change (''Joined: X. Left: Y''). Sending you a Loom of it now.</p>', 'Inline pill above the message that triggered the change (''Joined: X. Left: Y''). Sending you a Loom of it now.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1219200), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1219200), '[{"email":"deepa.rao@umbrella.med","name":"Deepa Rao"},{"email":"hugo.lefevre@umbrella.med","name":"Hugo Lefevre"},{"email":"petr.zelinka@umbrella.med","name":"Petr Zelinka"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_1a81a93e429517f7'),
  ('s_0068', 'p_g20', 'petr.zelinka@umbrella.med', 'support@example.com', 'Re: Chat-mode UI for support inboxes — feedback', '<p>Configurable keymap is a yes — we''ll ship default + Vim out of the box, with a JSON override for power users.</p>', 'Configurable keymap is a yes — we''ll ship default + Vim out of the box, with a JSON override for power users.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1138224), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1138224), '[{"email":"deepa.rao@umbrella.med","name":"Deepa Rao"},{"email":"hugo.lefevre@umbrella.med","name":"Hugo Lefevre"},{"email":"anika.osei@umbrella.med","name":"Anika Osei"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_1a81a93e429517f7'),
  ('s_0069', 'p_g19', 'anika.osei@umbrella.med', 'support@example.com', 'Re: Chat-mode UI for support inboxes — feedback', '<p>Good call, swapping the icon. Should be live in tomorrow''s deploy.</p>', 'Good call, swapping the icon. Should be live in tomorrow''s deploy.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1004857), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1004857), '[{"email":"deepa.rao@umbrella.med","name":"Deepa Rao"},{"email":"hugo.lefevre@umbrella.med","name":"Hugo Lefevre"},{"email":"petr.zelinka@umbrella.med","name":"Petr Zelinka"},{"email":"lin@example.com","name":"Lin Park"},{"email":"diego@example.com","name":"Diego Cruz"}]', 'c_1a81a93e429517f7'),
  ('s_0070', 'p_g09', 'priya.singh@procurement.globex.io', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: RFP response — Globex / Acme joint deployment', '<p>Thanks for including us. Will send our full RFP response by next Friday — let me know if there are any sections you''d like us to prioritize.</p>', 'Thanks for including us. Will send our full RFP response by next Friday — let me know if there are any sections you''d like us to prioritize.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1896601), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1896601), '[{"email":"olu.adebayo@globex.io","name":"Olu Adebayo"},{"email":"tariq.khan@legal.acme.co","name":"Tariq Khan"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"}]', 'c_eb8f309dcca13e8a'),
  ('s_0071', 'p_g21', 'olu.adebayo@globex.io', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: RFP response — Globex / Acme joint deployment', '<p>Noted — we''ll lead with those two. Quick question for residency: do you have a hard requirement for EU-only or is EU-primary with US-failover acceptable?</p>', 'Noted — we''ll lead with those two. Quick question for residency: do you have a hard requirement for EU-only or is EU-primary with US-failover acceptable?', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1743843), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1743843), '[{"email":"priya.singh@procurement.globex.io","name":"Priya Singh"},{"email":"tariq.khan@legal.acme.co","name":"Tariq Khan"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"}]', 'c_eb8f309dcca13e8a'),
  ('s_0072', 'p_g22', 'tariq.khan@legal.acme.co', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: RFP response — Globex / Acme joint deployment', '<p>All set on Art. 28(3). RFP response delivered today. Sections 4 and 6 are the first 18 pages.</p>', 'All set on Art. 28(3). RFP response delivered today. Sections 4 and 6 are the first 18 pages.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1289228), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1289228), '[{"email":"priya.singh@procurement.globex.io","name":"Priya Singh"},{"email":"olu.adebayo@globex.io","name":"Olu Adebayo"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"}]', 'c_eb8f309dcca13e8a'),
  ('s_0073', 'p_g21', 'olu.adebayo@globex.io', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: RFP response — Globex / Acme joint deployment', '<p>Multi-tenant ingress with per-tenant routing — page 9 description is correct, the diagram label was stale. Updated diagram attached.</p>', 'Multi-tenant ingress with per-tenant routing — page 9 description is correct, the diagram label was stale. Updated diagram attached.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1075313), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1075313), '[{"email":"priya.singh@procurement.globex.io","name":"Priya Singh"},{"email":"tariq.khan@legal.acme.co","name":"Tariq Khan"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"}]', 'c_eb8f309dcca13e8a'),
  ('s_0074', 'p_g09', 'priya.singh@procurement.globex.io', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: RFP response — Globex / Acme joint deployment', '<p>Tuesday works. We''ll bring our solutions architect and have a live demo of the multi-region setup.</p>', 'Tuesday works. We''ll bring our solutions architect and have a live demo of the multi-region setup.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 664600), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 664600), '[{"email":"olu.adebayo@globex.io","name":"Olu Adebayo"},{"email":"tariq.khan@legal.acme.co","name":"Tariq Khan"},{"email":"pavel@example.com","name":"Pavel Novak"}]', 'c_eb8f309dcca13e8a'),
  ('s_0075', 'p_g24', 'soren.bakke@hooli.com', 'hello@example.com', 'Re: Co-marketing webinar — joint Q&A format', '<p>Love the panel format. Proposing 4 panelists (one per company plus a moderator), 30 minutes panel, 20 minutes Q&A, 10 minutes wrap. Mid-November target?</p>', 'Love the panel format. Proposing 4 panelists (one per company plus a moderator), 30 minutes panel, 20 minutes Q&A, 10 minutes wrap. Mid-November target?', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1616426), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1616426), '[{"email":"wren.callahan@piedpiper.ai","name":"Wren Callahan"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_6a16bdb30c9e7e1e'),
  ('s_0076', 'p_g23', 'wren.callahan@piedpiper.ai', 'hello@example.com', 'Re: Co-marketing webinar — joint Q&A format', '<p>Sold. Drafting the run-of-show this week and will share for review. We''ll also handle the registration page.</p>', 'Sold. Drafting the run-of-show this week and will share for review. We''ll also handle the registration page.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1410091), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1410091), '[{"email":"soren.bakke@hooli.com","name":"Soren Bakke"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_6a16bdb30c9e7e1e'),
  ('s_0077', 'p_g24', 'soren.bakke@hooli.com', 'hello@example.com', 'Re: Co-marketing webinar — joint Q&A format', '<p>Unified landing with all three logos and per-company UTM tags so we can each track signups. Fair?</p>', 'Unified landing with all three logos and per-company UTM tags so we can each track signups. Fair?', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1379095), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1379095), '[{"email":"wren.callahan@piedpiper.ai","name":"Wren Callahan"},{"email":"maya@example.com","name":"Maya Iyer"},{"email":"ren@example.com","name":"Ren O''Brien"}]', 'c_6a16bdb30c9e7e1e'),
  ('s_0078', 'p_g00', 'elena.varga@acme.co', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: Consolidating three Acme business units onto one tenant', '<p>Three options: (1) lift-and-shift each in turn, (2) parallel-run with gradual cutover, (3) net-new tenant with read-only archives. Most customers in your shape pick (2).</p>', 'Three options: (1) lift-and-shift each in turn, (2) parallel-run with gradual cutover, (3) net-new tenant with read-only archives. Most customers in your shape pick (2).', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 2133698), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 2133698), '[{"email":"yuki.sato@orbis.health","name":"Yuki Sato"},{"email":"bo.westwood@vandelay.imp","name":"Bo Westwood"},{"email":"sam@example.com","name":"Sam Liu"}]', 'c_add97e9de41b6fa3'),
  ('s_0079', 'p_g25', 'yuki.sato@orbis.health', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: Consolidating three Acme business units onto one tenant', '<p>Yes — the archive lives on the same HIPAA-eligible tier as production. We sign a BAA covering both.</p>', 'Yes — the archive lives on the same HIPAA-eligible tier as production. We sign a BAA covering both.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1986138), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1986138), '[{"email":"elena.varga@acme.co","name":"Elena Varga"},{"email":"bo.westwood@vandelay.imp","name":"Bo Westwood"},{"email":"sam@example.com","name":"Sam Liu"}]', 'c_add97e9de41b6fa3'),
  ('s_0080', 'p_g26', 'bo.westwood@vandelay.imp', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: Consolidating three Acme business units onto one tenant', '<p>Vandelay last makes sense. The MX swap is independent of consolidation — we''ll script the cutover so it''s ~2 minutes of TTL-bounded propagation.</p>', 'Vandelay last makes sense. The MX swap is independent of consolidation — we''ll script the cutover so it''s ~2 minutes of TTL-bounded propagation.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1793680), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1793680), '[{"email":"elena.varga@acme.co","name":"Elena Varga"},{"email":"yuki.sato@orbis.health","name":"Yuki Sato"},{"email":"sam@example.com","name":"Sam Liu"}]', 'c_add97e9de41b6fa3'),
  ('s_0081', 'p_g00', 'elena.varga@acme.co', 'sales@example.com', 'Re: Consolidating three Acme business units onto one tenant', '<p>Locked in. Sending project plan + per-phase runbook. Kickoff call for Acme phase next Wednesday.</p>', 'Locked in. Sending project plan + per-phase runbook. Kickoff call for Acme phase next Wednesday.', NULL, 'sent', (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1380384), (CAST(strftime('%s','now') AS INTEGER) - 1380384), '[{"email":"yuki.sato@orbis.health","name":"Yuki Sato"},{"email":"bo.westwood@vandelay.imp","name":"Bo Westwood"},{"email":"sam@example.com","name":"Sam Liu"}]', 'c_add97e9de41b6fa3');

